        "rich_text_njtbcx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>What is a Lab Grown Diamond?</h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_eYEUa6": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_DjXatq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>More than gemstones, diamonds symbolize dreams, hope, and achievement. Diamond-buyers today want more than stunning designs; they seek beauty with values, and Lab Grown Diamonds fit the bill. But what is a Lab Grown Diamond? Are they real? Do they shine like natural ones?</p><p>Lab Grown Diamonds are 100% real, offering the same sparkle and brilliance as mined ones. Made in labs, they are special as they come without the environmental cost or ethical concerns.  In this blog, we’ll explore everything you need to know about Lab Grown Diamonds, decoding HPHT or what the CVD diamond process is, the myths surrounding them, and why they’re emerging as a popular choice.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_WBAdXE": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Defining Lab Grown Diamonds ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Defining Lab Grown Diamonds </h2>",
            "custom_id": "defining"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WMqYQp": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/LGD.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Lab Grown Diamond definition refers to the gemstones made by people, not nature. Also known as man-made or synthetic diamonds, they are grown under controlled lab conditions that mimic Earth’s natural process. While chemically, physically, structurally, and visually they share the same properties as the natural diamonds, the difference between the two boils down to their origin:</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_m6hCtt": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Natural diamonds develop over millions of years under Earth’s heat and pressure.</li><li>Lab Grown Diamonds grow in labs within weeks through advanced technology.</li></ul><p>So, you get a beautiful, genuine, and real diamond that’s kinder to the planet and often easier on your budget.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6xeeFQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How Are Lab Grown Diamonds Made?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How Are Lab Grown Diamonds Made?</h2><p>The creation of Lab Grown Diamond starts with a tiny \"diamond seed\", a thin slice of real diamond about as fine as a human hair. From this seed, diamonds grow using one of two methods:</p>",
            "custom_id": "howmade"
          }
        },
        "image_XjPbkw": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/CVD_vs_HPHT.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7XdJQJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>HPHT (High Pressure High Temperature): HPHT mimics the intense heat and pressure found deep inside the Earth. The diamond seed is placed in a machine where carbon melts around it, growing the diamond layer by layer over a few weeks. HPHT can also enhance the color of natural diamonds.</li><li>CVD (Chemical Vapor Deposition): Under CVD, a gas-based process, the seed is placed in a chamber containing carbon-rich gas. When exposed to intense heat and pressure, the gas breaks down, while carbon atoms attach to the seed, building the diamond layer by layer. </li></ul><p>While HPHT melts carbon like nature’s process, CVD grows diamonds atom by atom, offering more control over quality and shape.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        }
      },
